<div class="why-section">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="main-section">
      <div class="desc">
        <h2>Why this Course</h2>
        <div style="text-align:left">
          <p>This Executive MBA is completely delivered online, through a combination of pre-recorded lectures
            followed by well-developed learning materials along with a dedicated Personal Tutor support. The
            students gain flexibility of learning while maintaining access to face time with the tutors
            through the synchronous live online sessions.</p>

          <h5><strong>Highlights of this course are:</strong></h5>

          <ul>
            <li>This is triple certification program, Executive MBA from UCAM, Spain, Diploma from CIQ, UK
              and a Certified Manager certification from CMI, UK (optional)</li>
            <li>The program consists of 60 ECTS Credits</li>
            <li>Universidad Catolica De Murcia (UCAM) Spain, accredited by Ministry of Education, Spain, is
              a member of Bologna Process in European Higher Education Area (EHEA) and It is also a NARIC
              approved university</li>
            <li>The course delivery and assessments are based on real life situations and application which
              will directly benefit the learner at their workplace to improve their performance</li>
            <li>The course is designed to provide you with a range of knowledge which is crucial to lead a
              business organisation. The program&nbsp;aims to provide you with skills and business acumen
              to be successful in different domains of business.</li>
            <li>Option to attend the annual convocation conducted by the University at Murcia, Spain</li>
          </ul>

        </div>
        <p>Build your skills in all areas of managing and leading organizations</p>
      </div>
      <div class="forms">
        <div class="container-fluid p-0 about-us-wrapper form">
          <div class="course-login-wrapper">
            <div class="login-details">
              <h2>Still Not Sure ?</h2>
              <h3>Speak to an Advisor<span>&nbsp;</span></h3>
              <p>Not sure if this course is right for you? Fill in your details below and one of our
                Course Advisors will be in contact to provide you with the information you need to make
                a decision.</p>
                 <form id="registration-afpage" class="needs-validation" novalidate method="post">
            <div class="reg-form">
              <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                  <span for="firstName">First Name</span>
                  <input type="text" name="firstName" class="form-control reg-form-control" id="firstName"
                    placeholder="First Name" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                  <span for="lastName">Last Name</span>
                  <input type="text" name="lastName" class="form-control reg-form-control" id="lastName"
                    placeholder="Last Name" required>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-row regUserEmail">
                <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                  <span for="regEmail">Email</span>
                  <input type="email" name="regEmail" class="form-control reg-form-control" id="regEmail"
                    pattern="[a-z0-9._%+-]+@[a-z0-9.-]+\.[a-z]{2,3}$" placeholder="Email" required>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-row phone-number">
                <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                  <span for="reg_mobile_num">Phone Number</span>
                  <input type="tel" id="reg_mobile_num" name="reg_mobile_num" class="reg-form-control"
                    placeholder="Enter Mobile number" required>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                  <span for="highestQualification">Highest Qualification</span>
                  <select id="highestQualification" name="highestQualification" class="form-control reg-form-control"
                    required>
                    <option value="">Select your highest qualification</option>
                    <option value="Masters Degree">Masters Degree</option>
                    <option value="Bachelors Degree">Bachelors Degree</option>
                    <option value="Diploma">Diploma</option>
                    <option value="A Level">A Level</option>
                    <option value="Others">Others</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="form-row" style="display:none;">
                <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                  <span for="course">Course</span>
                  <select name="course" id="course" class="form-control reg-form-control" required>
                    <option value="{{course_info.cid}}" selected="selected">{{course_info.cid}}</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!--<div class="form-group text-center form-check consent-check">-->
              <div class="form-group text-center consent-check">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="terms" name="terms[]">
                <span class="form-check-label terms-label" for="terms">I agree with <a href="/registration-terms"
                    target="_blank">Terms &amp; Conditions</a></span>

                <button type="button" class="btn btn-pink sign-up-button">{% if payment %} Enrol Now {% else %} Sign Up {% endif %}</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ref-form-2" id="ref-form-2" style="display: none;">
              <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                <span for="pswd">Password</span>
                <input type="password" name="pswd" class="form-control reg-form-control" id="pswd"
                  placeholder="Password" required autocomplete="off">
                <div class="invalid-feedback">
                  Please enter a password
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group col-md-12">
                <span for="confirmpswd">Confirm Password</span>
                <input type="password" name="confirmpswd" class="form-control reg-form-control" id="confirmpswd"
                  placeholder="Re-enter Password" required autocomplete="off">
                <div class="invalid-feedback confirm-password">
                  Please enter password again
                </div>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-pink" style="width:100%;margin-top:0px">Register</button>
            </div>
            <input id="cId" name="cId" type="hidden" value="">
            <input id="modId" name="modId" type="hidden" value="">
            <input id="countryId" name="countryId" type="hidden" value="">

            {% if payment %}
              <input id="pay" name="pay" type="hidden" value="{{ payment }}">
            {% else %}
              <input id="pay" name="pay" type="hidden" value="">
            {% endif %}

          </form>
              
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
